Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.78,0:00:03.56,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,小岛  你要是一块巧克力都没收到的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.61,0:00:04.76,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我就分你一点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.96,0:00:06.87,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不不  我已经收到两块了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.69,0:00:07.42,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}早上好  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.44,0:00:08.46,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}你骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.91,0:00:09.45,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,今天是情人节呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.62,0:00:11.04,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我开始紧张了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.06,0:00:12.10,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.41,0:00:12.92,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,2月14日  在这人人为之兴奋的节日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.59,0:00:18.77,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同学今年肯定也会乘此机会来捉弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.53,0:00:20.34,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.78,0:00:23.26,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我不能被她迷惑了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.11,0:00:26.47,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.79,0:00:28.08,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不愧是高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.10,0:00:29.80,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,还准备了三份
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.01,0:00:32.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但是  你还太嫩了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.77,0:00:35.43,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,反正就像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.96,0:00:38.20,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,或是像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.77,0:00:41.73,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,又或是像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.25,0:00:44.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我早就看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.78,0:00:46.64,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,来吧  放马过来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.19,0:00:53.44,Takagi san—Picture 11-1,,0,0,0,,{\frz312.4\pos(1138,624)\fs90\t(0,6000,\fs110)}致学长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.05,0:00:51.21,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,包装得还真精致呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.92,0:00:52.80,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,致学长？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.14,0:00:55.78,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.71,0:01:00.14,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,完全搞不懂高木同学想怎么捉弄人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.74,0:01:03.42,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,话说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.21,0:01:06.41,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,哪一封看上去都不像是高木同学写的字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.14,0:01:12.06,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,给学长  我在文化祭的时候喜欢上你了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.79,0:01:11.88,Takagi san—Picture 11-1,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\pos(902,420)}致学长
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.79,0:01:11.88,Takagi san—Picture 11-1,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\an1\pos(492,738)}我在文化祭的\N时候喜欢上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.79,0:01:11.88,Takagi san—Picture 11-1,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\pos(742,902)}请收下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.17,0:01:19.61,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,难道说  这不是高木同学送的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.80,0:01:20.97,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,而是学妹送的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.66,0:01:23.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,而且还有三份
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.68,0:01:32.00,Takagi san—OP-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}目が合うずっと前から まっすぐ見ていたのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.72,0:01:45.73,Takagi san—OP-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}昨日までの教室とは ちょっと違う気がする理由
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.04,0:01:58.14,Takagi san—OP-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}世界中で二人だけ 知っている秘密こと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.46,0:02:06.38,Takagi san—OP-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}空色のハンカチは今日もポケットの中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.72,0:02:12.72,Takagi san—OP-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}もどかしそうにしてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.38,0:02:20.44,Takagi san—OP-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}目が合うずっと前から まっすぐ見ていたもの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.66,0:02:26.22,Takagi san—OP-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}届いてしまいそうな間際で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.84,0:02:39.11,Takagi san—OP-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}何度も言葉にして 私なりの形で 思いを伝えてきたから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.12,0:02:48.60,Takagi san—OP-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}ねえ　これからは素直なままで受け取ってみて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.68,0:01:32.00,Takagi san—OP-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}在我们四目相视以前 我就一直看着你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.72,0:01:45.73,Takagi san—OP-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}今天的教室和昨天有所不同的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.04,0:01:58.14,Takagi san—OP-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}是有了这世界上只有我们两人知道的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.46,0:02:06.38,Takagi san—OP-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}天蓝色的手帕今天也在口袋中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.72,0:02:12.72,Takagi san—OP-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}躁动不安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.38,0:02:20.44,Takagi san—OP-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}因为在我们四目相视以前 我就一直看着你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.66,0:02:26.22,Takagi san—OP-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}每当我们即将对视
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.84,0:02:39.11,Takagi san—OP-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}我都无数次地用我的言语 我的方式 把心意传达给你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.12,0:02:48.60,Takagi san—OP-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}呐  从今往后要和我真情相待喔
