Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.40,0:03:01.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,悄悄地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.82,0:03:10.78,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,早上好  西片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.01,0:03:14.25,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,早上好  高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:18.71,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,今天也来得非常早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.35,0:03:20.45,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯  有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.88,0:03:22.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,久违地骑自行车来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.90,0:03:24.21,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是这样呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.03,0:03:28.25,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可不能让高木同学问起巧克力的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:29.37,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我说西片…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.56,0:03:31.81,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,今天是几号来着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.93,0:03:34.21,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我不能慌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.05,0:03:38.94,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同学会像这样拿情人节来捉弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.46,0:03:42.22,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,明明昨天就已经预料到了  不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.83,0:03:46.73,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我已经想好了该怎么回敬她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:50.23,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯  今天是2月14日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.39,0:03:51.35,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是小鱼干日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.81,0:03:55.08,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你知道吗  高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:03:57.92,Takagi san—Picture 11-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1094,994)}                    ni    ichi   yon
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:03:57.92,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,在黑板上写上「2」「1」「4」看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.49,0:03:58.82,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.74,0:04:04.34,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.82,0:04:06.72,Takagi san—Picture 11-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1068,996)}               bo-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.82,0:04:06.72,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,把「1」读作棒的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.89,0:04:08.45,Takagi san—Picture 11-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1026,994)}         niboshi
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.89,0:04:08.45,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,就会念成小鱼干了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.89,0:04:08.45,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs60}注：数字4在日语中既能读作yon也能读作shi
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:10.88,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,数字的谐音梗呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.61,0:04:12.64,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,有些牵强就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.22,0:04:15.83,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但是  这是正式的纪念日哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.47,0:04:17.38,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,话说西片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.55,0:04:20.02,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你刚刚是不是想藏什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.30,0:04:21.70,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不  没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.68,0:04:24.88,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不愧是高木同学  真敏锐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.45,0:04:28.28,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不继续岔开话题的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.28,0:04:31.18,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.65,0:04:35.53,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,为了庆祝小鱼干日  我们用谐音梗来对话怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.57,0:04:38.87,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,用谐音梗来对话？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.66,0:04:42.47,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,没错  那么先从我开始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.24,0:04:48.37,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,猜错了就算输
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.71,0:04:51.20,Takagi san—Picture 11-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(934,994)}ohayou
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.71,0:04:51.20,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,早上好？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.84,0:04:51.20,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs60\fad(500,450)}注：这里0当作o，8念作ha，4念作yon即与「早上好」相似
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.21,0:04:51.69,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这么快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.40,0:04:53.37,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,咦  我说对了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.42,0:04:56.71,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这个可能太简单了点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.24,0:04:59.13,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好了  下面轮到高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.70,0:05:00.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.76,0:05:03.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,看我一下给你猜出来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.24,0:05:08.53,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,情…人…节？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.73,0:05:14.97,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,原来不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.94,0:05:16.42,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我写好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.85,0:05:22.13,Takagi san—Picture 11-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1186,992)}                      barebare
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.85,0:05:22.13,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,太简单了  答案是完全暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.93,0:05:28.70,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,意思是  我偷藏巧克力的事情完全暴露了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.61,0:05:30.17,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.54,0:05:32.14,Takagi san—Picture 11-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1070,994)}      harebare
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.54,0:05:32.14,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,答案是  晴朗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.71,0:05:36.62,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我是想告诉你今天是个晴朗的好天气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.28,0:05:42.23,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,用谐音梗来表达真难呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.63,0:05:43.54,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.68,0:05:45.00,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,吓死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.43,0:05:46.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,虽说有些模棱两可
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.68,0:05:48.90,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但是可以算西片猜错输了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.86,0:05:50.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.76,0:05:52.42,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,还好没猜对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:55.90,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那么惩罚游戏  要让你做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.93,0:06:02.09,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,话说  为什么我要拼命向高木同学隐瞒巧克力的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.10,0:06:04.17,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.58,0:06:08.65,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,明明只要跟她说  其实有学妹送我巧克力就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.53,0:06:13.82,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,对了  让我看看作业就行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.54,0:06:17.38,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,作业？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.02,0:06:18.29,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.16,0:06:21.48,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,有一个问题想向你请教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.77,0:06:24.09,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可以倒是可以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.82,0:06:26.72,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这就是输了比赛的惩罚游戏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:28.64,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真少见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:30.57,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同学竟然会向我请教作业
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:34.70,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,现在把包打开的话  巧克力会被看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.14,0:06:36.73,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.84,0:06:41.75,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,事到如今  还是向高木同学坦白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.72,0:06:45.90,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,她可能还会和我讨论一下我该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.25,0:06:49.28,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同学  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.75,0:06:50.40,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,还是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.91,0:06:55.56,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可能我是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.03,0:06:57.76,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.76,0:07:00.86,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,坦白的时机…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.28,0:07:03.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,话说回来  要是平时的高木同学的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:05.50,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,会更变本加厉地捉弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.12,0:07:07.12,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,会找到巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:10.47,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,然后哈哈大笑才对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.52,0:07:22.72,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,情人节快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:23.77,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,情人节快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.00,0:07:25.42,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你这是打的什么招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.59,0:07:30.32,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我觉得情人节跟圣诞节差不多快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:34.07,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,所以  圣诞老人美奈要送你们礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.52,0:07:37.64,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,今年只为你俩用心准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.08,0:07:38.61,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.20,0:07:48.96,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我们三人间的友情有着比巧克力更坚硬的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.14,0:07:51.05,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这份礼物里蕴含着我的这份心意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:54.30,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,美奈  你竟然把我们看得这么重要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.63,0:07:57.54,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但是  友情的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.24,0:07:59.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,已经融化得不成样子了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.08,0:08:02.82,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.95,0:08:05.70,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我明明记得我放进冰箱了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.08,0:08:07.37,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是不是因为这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.47,0:08:13.96,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,早上还以为不见了  原来在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:15.96,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,暖宝宝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.25,0:08:19.20,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我明明那么努力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.67,0:08:21.16,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不用哭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.98,0:08:23.64,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这样也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.88,0:08:26.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,友情融为一体  三人一体的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.97,0:08:27.99,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,看起来也很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.29,0:08:30.20,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.78,0:08:31.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.12,0:08:33.35,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好啦  我也有东西要送给你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:35.19,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,虽然不是亲手做的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.92,0:08:46.73,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,果然是三个臭皮匠顶个诸葛亮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.62,0:08:48.82,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,情人节快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.77,0:09:05.84,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,中井  这个送你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.16,0:09:08.40,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,哦  难道说是巧克力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.56,0:09:10.94,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嘘  你声音太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.30,0:09:13.00,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,会被田边老师听到的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.58,0:09:14.72,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,对不起对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.80,0:09:16.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,情人节…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.22,0:09:17.99,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.18,0:09:19.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.64,0:09:21.28,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,滨口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.98,0:09:25.46,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你想要巧克力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.07,0:09:31.44,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,如果你愿意给我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:33.40,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是么  给你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.70,0:09:39.93,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,快点收下啊  老师会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.53,0:09:43.09,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.13,0:09:45.42,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.83,0:09:50.69,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.27,0:09:54.46,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这个…不是亲手做的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.13,0:09:59.45,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,昨天我刚好在超市看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:03.21,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,北条在买做巧克力的材料
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.73,0:10:06.92,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,如果她没有送我亲手做的巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.06,0:10:10.58,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,意思就是那才是本命巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.47,0:10:14.33,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,给了我以外的某个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.37,0:10:17.04,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,有得拿就不错了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.29,0:10:18.85,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我替你吃掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.08,0:10:20.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,安慰我一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.90,0:10:23.51,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,比较级的词尾加「er」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.15,0:10:27.22,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,最高级的词尾加「est」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.05,0:10:30.56,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但是  有几个例外
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.32,0:10:36.29,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}比如「beatiful」之类比较长的形容词
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.68,0:10:34.26,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:39.29,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,比较级加上「more」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:40.82,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,成为「more beatiful」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.65,0:10:43.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}最高级加上「most」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:45.94,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那个西片  讲到其他页了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.04,0:10:46.22,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}变成「most beatiful」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.87,0:10:54.20,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.53,0:10:55.73,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,如果是平时的高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.02,0:11:00.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,应该会设下一堆情人节专属的圈套才对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.27,0:11:04.92,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这样就找不到和她说巧克力那事的机会了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.38,0:11:07.06,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.70,0:11:09.29,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那就由我出手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.70,0:11:11.52,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我说高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.41,0:11:13.53,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,要不要和我比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.21,0:11:14.93,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎么比
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.04,0:11:18.00,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,比橡皮擦屑的长度
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.64,0:11:22.41,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,像这样擦到它断掉为止
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.89,0:11:24.17,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,擦得长的人算赢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:27.13,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可以是可以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:32.56,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这招我还没练到家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.88,0:11:36.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,原本计划等到擦出2.5厘米的屑以后再向她挑战的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.96,0:11:44.52,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但这里要抛下自尊故意输给她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.02,0:11:45.67,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.82,0:11:49.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,耶  我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.82,0:11:51.14,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我输了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.22,0:11:51.89,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.00,0:11:52.85,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,作为惩罚游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.91,0:11:55.81,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,只好不情愿地把我的秘密告诉高木同学了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:11:57.58,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这是什么这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.66,0:12:00.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这样就很自然了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.44,0:12:02.74,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那可以从我开始吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.33,0:12:03.76,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.85,0:12:09.20,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,哎呀  好难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.62,0:12:11.32,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这样下去感觉要输
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.97,0:12:13.17,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,毕竟是高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.30,0:12:15.82,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,肯定会捉弄我来捣乱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.97,0:12:18.16,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.05,0:12:23.43,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.11,0:12:28.26,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,3.5厘米
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.64,0:12:30.64,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,大幅刷新自己的记录了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.45,0:12:34.17,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,为什么非要在想输的时候超常发挥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.37,0:12:35.10,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,很厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.70,0:12:36.64,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,恭喜你西片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.72,0:12:39.59,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你怎么回事  高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.73,0:12:41.01,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,为什么不来捉弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.21,0:12:42.14,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,接下来到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.37,0:12:43.19,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.84,0:12:44.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.52,0:12:45.88,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真的请你加把劲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.29,0:12:48.01,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同学的话应该能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.74,0:12:51.11,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不错哦  就是这样高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.64,0:12:52.34,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我说啊西片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.96,0:12:54.28,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,如果我赢了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.77,0:12:56.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,当…当然  我什么都会做的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.68,0:12:57.44,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.78,0:13:01.38,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那作为惩罚  我坦白一个秘密怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.03,0:13:04.79,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,果然今天还是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.34,0:13:08.87,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同学竟然会放弃比赛  真是难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.04,0:13:10.39,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是不是要下大雪了…不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.66,0:13:12.93,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,什么雪啊  简直是要下陨石了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.13,0:13:16.33,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,别这样  加把劲嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.88,0:13:18.25,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,需要加把劲的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.29,0:13:23.72,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,「beautiful」的比较级和最高级是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.05,0:13:27.42,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,beautifuler  beautifulest
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.49,0:13:29.92,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片  你果然没听课吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.32,0:13:31.86,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:35.67,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真是的  这里会考的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.82,0:13:37.20,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,别忘了复习
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.54,0:13:38.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.85,0:13:44.10,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,太好了  是平时的高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.85,0:13:48.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,樱井同学很高兴地收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.49,0:13:50.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,快回来  别让他们得分了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.51,0:13:53.61,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,喂  放学去趟零食店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.69,0:13:56.45,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好啊  自掏腰包狂吃巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.29,0:14:01.03,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,必须跟高木同学说才行…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.53,0:14:02.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,打扰一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.25,0:14:04.76,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片学长在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.47,0:14:09.22,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片  有人找你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.22,0:14:18.71,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.69,0:14:22.80,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那个…学长  我们的巧克力…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.11,0:14:23.96,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,巧克力？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.87,0:14:25.99,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你这个叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.72,0:14:28.02,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是说这些吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.64,0:14:32.41,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.44,0:14:34.54,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.71,0:14:39.48,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片  连你也加入那边的阵营了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.68,0:14:40.95,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真好啊  竟然有三份
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.53,0:14:42.82,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,然后我给了爸爸后…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.74,0:14:46.30,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但是对不起  我不能收下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.58,0:14:53.57,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,虽然我特别高兴  但…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.45,0:14:55.77,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.01,0:14:58.86,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.90,0:14:59.13,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.56,0:15:03.05,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,其实我们搞错了鞋柜的位置  放错地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:06.85,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真是的  都怪你说学长的鞋柜就在那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.10,0:15:09.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,抱歉  看错了一行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.85,0:15:11.57,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.30,0:15:13.96,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.28,0:15:17.91,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可以麻烦你叫下柴崎学长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.17,0:15:22.57,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,柴崎学长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:25.37,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你在文化祭演的小狗真的很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.43,0:15:29.03,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那个  请收下我们的巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.12,0:15:29.81,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.18,0:15:33.29,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你早点吃掉就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.61,0:15:34.14,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.65,0:15:35.62,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.12,0:15:39.46,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这下就不必向高木同学保留多余的秘密了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.52,0:15:43.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,说起来高木同学去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.37,0:15:56.92,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,天空好澄澈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.88,0:16:00.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嘴巴干嘛张这么大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.36,0:16:02.01,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,北条
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.26,0:16:04.74,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,跟僵尸一样怪吓人的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.14,0:16:06.14,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,建议你别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.25,0:16:09.99,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,所以  你在消沉什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.57,0:16:12.07,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我才没有消沉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.40,0:16:13.12,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,少骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.58,0:16:16.00,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你只要做这个动作就是在消沉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.01,0:16:19.16,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.09,0:16:21.99,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你觉得我们有多少年的交情了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.48,0:16:24.63,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,啊我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.81,0:16:27.34,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,因为收到的巧克力少得可怜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.87,0:16:32.47,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,北条怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.96,0:16:36.16,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,本命巧克力  有好好送出去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.29,0:16:37.85,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,本命？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.33,0:16:39.57,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不用瞒着我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.16,0:16:41.52,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你有亲手做巧克力的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.77,0:16:44.34,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,为什么你会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.03,0:16:47.93,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我在超市偶然看到你在买材料
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.01,0:16:55.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,全…全都融化掉失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.42,0:16:59.00,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我就少盯了一会儿而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.35,0:17:01.43,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,为什么会融化得那么快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.50,0:17:05.20,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.42,0:17:07.89,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我的失败就那么好笑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.16,0:17:09.38,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,啊  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.04,0:17:12.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,算了  你恢复精神了就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.97,0:17:14.63,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.58,0:17:18.31,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,也就是说  给我的巧克力是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.78,0:17:23.12,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,白色情人节请给我高级的巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.50,0:17:25.22,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,啊…好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.58,0:17:33.14,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,对啊  今年没有收到高木同学的巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:40.69,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,话说我才没有在期待
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.64,0:17:42.38,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.72,0:18:03.72,Takagi san—Picture 11-3,,0,0,0,,{\frz355.3\pos(556,892)}明天能早点来学校吗？我有东西想给你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:09.02,Takagi san—Picture 11-3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(582,896)\frz354.7}明天早点来学校的话可能会有好事发生哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.11,0:18:14.27,Takagi san—Picture 11-3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(410,884)\frz354.7}有什么想要的东西吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.66,0:18:22.91,Takagi san—Picture 11-3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(812,230)\frz355.8}现在能见上一面吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.72,0:18:30.44,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.36,0:18:46.06,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真巧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.78,0:18:49.29,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,因为看到你自行车停在那
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.20,0:18:50.77,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.30,0:18:57.45,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那…那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:19:01.08,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,其实今天我收到来自学妹的巧克力了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.78,0:19:03.59,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,最后好像是搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.77,0:19:07.18,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不是给我而是要给柴崎的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.72,0:19:11.13,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但我是想跟高木同学说我收到巧克力这件事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.56,0:19:13.69,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,却迟迟开不了口  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.84,0:19:14.54,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.58,0:19:15.82,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,欸  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:16.41,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.72,0:19:17.64,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,搞啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.33,0:19:20.40,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,害得我一直心里不踏实
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.94,0:19:21.75,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.12,0:19:25.45,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我也一直在忐忑不安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.72,0:19:31.40,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我不太想听西片跟我说收到巧克力的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.33,0:19:37.33,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,感觉一旦听了  又会变成之前那个坏心眼的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.30,0:19:39.91,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我不想变成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.22,0:19:44.31,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,然后就不能顺利捉弄西片了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.69,0:19:48.20,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,有点讨厌那样的自己呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.38,0:19:53.03,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.84,0:19:57.89,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不  该道歉的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.10,0:19:59.73,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,让你心情变糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.26,0:20:08.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,奇怪  高木同学怎么知道我收到巧克力了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.66,0:20:10.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.85,0:20:11.99,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,给  西片
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.90,0:20:19.11,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,其实我早上就想放到西片的鞋柜里了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.50,0:20:22.42,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,虽然觉得明天再给也行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.11,0:20:25.67,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但还是想在2月14号这天送给你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.21,0:20:28.41,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你能收下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.89,0:20:34.05,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,谢…谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.06,0:20:38.69,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我可以打开吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.73,0:20:43.99,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.21,0:20:45.93,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,小鱼干？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.77,0:20:49.20,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,2月14号是小鱼干日对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.72,0:20:52.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可恶的高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.89,0:20:58.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片说小鱼干日的时候  我好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.58,0:21:01.34,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我们的想法渐渐相近了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.26,0:21:03.12,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,因为在一起的时间太长了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.53,0:21:09.32,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这个是给猫咪的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.93,0:21:10.30,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.71,0:21:11.69,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片的是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.17,0:21:14.96,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.17,0:21:18.84,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,太好了  能在2月14号这天送到你手上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.75,0:21:21.51,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,心情总算是转晴了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.45,0:21:25.96,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,喂  橡皮擦的比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.17,0:21:27.03,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,明天再来一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.96,0:21:28.41,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.68,0:21:30.72,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不过赢的肯定是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.82,0:21:32.53,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那种事谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.94,0:21:34.82,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可恶的高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.02,0:21:44.04,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎么了  滨口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.29,0:21:47.82,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,重要的事是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.30,0:21:51.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎么  你打算去表白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.62,0:21:52.07,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.31,0:21:56.97,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,白色情人节时我要跟北条表白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.46,0:21:57.96,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,表…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.07,0:22:00.90,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,所以西片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.73,0:22:04.34,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,到那天你就去跟高木同学表白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.92,0:22:05.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.27,0:22:12.02,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}スノーマジックファンタジー
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.19,0:22:15.82,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}雪の魔法にかけられて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.03,0:22:19.49,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}僕は君に恋した
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.63,0:22:24.52,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}もしかして君は雪の妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.92,0:22:28.69,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}君が住む山は「スノーランド」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.78,0:22:36.33,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}一年中雪の降るこの国で    私は生まれたのと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.66,0:22:39.56,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}君は話してくれたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.12,0:22:46.48,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}ねぇ    私は夏を見たことがないの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.54,0:22:56.44,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}燃えるようなあの夏を    それを見るのが私の夢なの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.55,0:22:58.93,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}でも良いの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.97,0:23:07.00,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}この世界は知らない方がロマンチックな事も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.52,0:23:13.24,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}たくさんあるのでしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.52,0:23:17.24,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}スノーマジックファンタジー
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.49,0:23:21.07,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}雪の魔法にかけられて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.29,0:23:24.73,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}僕は君に恋した
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.90,0:23:28.85,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}もしかして君は雪の精？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.98,0:23:37.25,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}雪の妖精とのファンタジー
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.27,0:22:12.02,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}snow magic fantasy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.19,0:22:15.82,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}被施加了雪之魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.03,0:22:19.49,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}我对你一见倾心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.63,0:22:24.52,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}难道你就是雪之妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.92,0:22:28.69,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}你住在名为「雪国」的大山
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.78,0:22:36.33,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}降生于终年飘雪的国度
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.66,0:22:39.56,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}你曾对我如是诉说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.12,0:22:46.48,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}呐  我从未见过盛夏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.54,0:22:56.44,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}看那炽热如火的盛夏  是我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.55,0:22:58.93,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}不过无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.97,0:23:07.00,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}在这个世界上还有许多
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.52,0:23:13.24,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}因为未知才有的浪漫对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.52,0:23:17.24,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}snow magic fantasy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.49,0:23:21.07,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}被施加了雪之魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.29,0:23:24.73,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}我对你一见倾心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.90,0:23:28.85,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}难道你是雪之妖精？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.98,0:23:37.25,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}与雪之妖精的幻想
